/*
1)Database/ApplicationUser.sql
2)Database/ApplicationRole.sql
3)Database/ApplicationUserRole.sql
4)WebApp/Models/ApplicationUser.cs
5)WebApp/Models/ApplicationRole.cs
6)WebApp/Data/UserStore.cs
7)WebApp/Data/RoleStore.cs
8)WebApp/Startup.cs (Specifically the first three lines in ConfigureServices()
